{"tid":2360740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾國衞：曾提醒初選或觸國安法，逾越紅線便要承擔後果   警方：暫不檢控","createTime":"2021-01-10T05:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T02:57:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dc433631e5e57f3c2fe28914c6aa20609ffc59b6","tid":2360740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569624-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569624-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=0a70cf98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569624-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e150bd2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569624-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方國安處日前以顛覆國家政權罪拘捕民主派53人，政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞表示，當時已用心良苦提醒他們初選可能觸犯國家安全法，但遺憾不獲理會，他們仍囂張繼續有關活動。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞接受中新社訪問時說，既然已立下規矩及劃下紅線，當然要按照規矩紅線執法，有些事情既然是不可逾越，但非要逾越的話，就要承擔法律後果。<br />\n<br />\n另外，曾國衞說，當局就完善公職人員宣誓安排的研究工作已進入尾聲，會盡快完成提交立法會審議。他說正研究把區議員納入有關規定，一旦有區議員違反參選時作出的聲明會被追究。<br />\n<br />\n他提到在本港反修例風波時，有人衝進立法會，有美國政要稱為「很和平的示威者」。但美國國會日前受衝擊，美方就指這是暴動和暴徒，質疑美方雙重標準。"},{"pid":"b0e4e71770693b7d27c6fd491addb22aa561e76d","tid":2360740,"uid":53922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"fucking Shed Crocodile Tears"},{"pid":"59397ec670721121b1519b22c0d82f67cfc10ad2","tid":2360740,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"一副奴材相,出嚟鳩up有無show錢㗎？！"},{"pid":"29b978ac7e08561fd0f88bbcb192bfebe7077aa7","tid":2360740,"uid":79302,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"佢張相個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />